    "describe how the dataset was collected and post-processed and discuss examples of potential research that could be achieved with the dataset.",
    "(8) Charades (Sigurdsson et al. 2016) Computer vision technology can help people in their daily lives by finding lost keys, watering plants, or reminding people to take their medicine.",
    "To accomplish these tasks, researchers need to train computer vision methods from real and diverse examples of everyday dynamic scenarios.",
    "Sigurdsson et al.",
    "proposed a novel Hollywood family approach to collecting such data."
